GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SalesDecks> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_SalesDecks> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#SalesDecks> ;
    narr:childCount "24"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "ef6aa9e4415a4968de5683bd13b7e5942e7b42a2" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of sales-as-delivery, where the act of selling is indistinguishable from the product itself. Early requests for [pre-read decks](narr:Position_PreReadDeckRequest) and [written sales guides](narr:Position_SalesGuideRequest) (Mar 2026) quickly shifted toward high-fidelity, visual-first demonstrations. The trajectory moved from static artifacts to [GIF-based materials](narr:Narrative_GIFBasedSalesMaterials) that simulate real product usage, exemplified by the [before/after money GIF](narr:Narrative_DemoGIFStory) and a [finalized four-step demo script](narr:Narrative_DemoScriptOutsideTechBetaUser). 

Central to this is the [podcast/interview as sales motion](narr:Narrative_PodcastInterviewSalesMotion), which collapses demo, onboarding, and content into one event. This serves as a [forcing function](narr:Narrative_InterviewForcingFunction) for human-driven development, ensuring product features remain reactionary to actual user needs. Tony Maley further extended this by proposing a [procedural sales motion](narr:Narrative_SellTheProcessPreCaseStudy) to engage enterprise prospects before formal case studies exist. The current emphasis is on [generosity as demonstration](narr:Narrative_GenerosityAsDemonstration), where unsolicited bespoke artifacts delivered within 48 hours of a call act as the primary conversion engine, replacing traditional pitch-based models with a [keep-it-running](narr:Narrative_KeepingBeatsStarting) conversion ask.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DemoGIFStory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DemoRepoNeeded> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DemoScriptOutsideTechBetaUser> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DocumentGenerationAsProductDemo> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GIFBasedSalesMaterials> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GenerosityAsDemonstration> ;
